gotodo version 0.2

A simple command-line todo list written in Go.

Installation:

1. Install Go:
    http://golang.org/doc/install.html

2. Install todo:
    $ go get github.com/jack-zh/gotodo

Usage:

    gotodo list
        Show all tasks
    gotodo list N
        Show task N
    gotodo rm N
        Remove task N
    gotodo done N
        Done task N
    gotodo undo N
        Undo task N
    gotodo doing N
        Doing task N
    gotodo clean
        Rm done task
    gotodo clear
        Rm all task
    gotodo add ...
        Add task to list

Next version 0.3:

1. update time
2. json file and data
    

